his is also"}, {"start": 1053.06, "dur": 0.991, "text": "basically a question"}, {"start": 1054.076, "dur": 1.862, "text": "How we divide in ranges?"}, {"start": 1055.962, "dur": 1.691, "text": "We have to write ranges along with that"}, {"start": 1057.681, "dur": 1.522, "text": "also to write direct broadcast address"}, {"start": 1059.228, "dur": 0.912, "text": "of each subnet"}, {"start": 1060.165, "dur": 2.02, "text": "network ID, direct broadcast address"}, {"start": 1062.21, "dur": 2.15, "text": "and at last subnet mask,"}, {"start": 1064.385, "dur": 1.413, "text": "so to write subnet mask"}, {"start": 1065.823, "dur": 1.721, "text": "all the table you have reserved"}, {"start": 1067.569, "dur": 1.949, "text": "that much bit you make as 1"}, {"start": 1069.543, "dur": 1.401, "text": "and the rest as it is"}, {"start": 1070.969, "dur": 1.538, "text": "you know what is default mask"}, {"start": 1072.532, "dur": 1.894, "text": "255.255.255"}, {"start": 1074.451, "dur": 2.38, "text": "if it is class B then according to class B"}, {"start": 1076.856, "dur": 1.816, "text": "if it is A then according to class A"}, {"start": 1078.697, "dur": 2.071, "text": "this is the basic funda of what?"}, {"start": 1080.793, "dur": 2.27, "text": "subnetting under classful"}, {"start": 1083.106, "dur": 2.135, "text": "at last let me tell you a small point"}, {"start": 1085.266, "dur": 1.031, "text": "the disadvantage,"}, {"start": 1086.322, "dur": 1.377, "text": "we had talked about advantage"}, {"start": 1087.724, "dur": 1.817, "text": "but not talked about disadvantage"}, {"start": 1089.566, "dur": 1.782, "text": "so what is the disadvantage?"}, {"start": 1091.373, "dur": 2.61, "text": "A small point students have to keep in mind"}, {"start": 1094.021, "dur": 2.5, "text": "we generally find IP address"}, {"start": 1096.546, "dur": 1.3, "text": "What are IP address?"}, {"start": 1097.871, "dur": 1.77, "text": "network ID"}, {"start": 1099.666, "dur": 1.372, "text": "and host ID"}, 